    <h4 id="sec-misc-9" class="text-lg font-semibold mt-6">6. CONCLUSION</h4>

    <p class="text-gray-300">We have presented HoneyBadgerBFT, the first efficient and highthroughput asynchronous BFT protocol. Through our implementation and experimental results we demonstrate that HoneyBadgerBFT can be a suitable component in incipient cryptocurrency-inspired deployments of fault tolerant transaction processing systems. More generally, we believe our work demonstrates the promise of building dependable and transaction processing systems based on asynchronous protocol.</p>

